          "reviewBody": "Prime Academy is a true beacon of education and inspiration. From the exceptional faculty to the cutting-edge facilities, this school offers an unparalleled learning experience. The emphasis on holistic development, the tight-knit community, and the integration of technology make Prime Academy a top-notch institution. I am proud to be part of this extraordinary school!",
