          },
          "reviewBody": "Very good school with all facilities. Amazing lunch and breakfast provided. The Principal Ms Rehana Kazi, Director Chaula Joshi and teaching staff are very approachable and open with parents. Their annual day and sports day ate out of the class with great learning for the students. Very neat and upto date school premises as well.",
